<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 03:18:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国最终确定审查军事基地附近更多外国土地交易的规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-finalizes-rule-review-more-foreign-land-deals-near-military-bases-2024-11-01/</link><description>拜登政府周五敲定了一项新规则，扩大了其审查外国购买美国军事基地附近房地产是否构成国家安全威胁的权力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 20:50:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-finalizes-rule-review-more-foreign-land-deals-near-military-bases-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>韩国部长表示正在考虑援助乌克兰的所有方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-minister-says-all-scenarios-under-consideration-aiding-ukraine-2024-11-01/</link><description>韩国外交部长赵太烈周五被问及首尔是否可以向乌克兰提供武器以回应朝鲜援助俄罗斯时表示，所有可能的情况都在考虑之中。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 20:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-minister-says-all-scenarios-under-consideration-aiding-ukraine-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>格罗方德因向受制裁的中国公司运送芯片而被美国罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-penalizes-globalfoundries-shipping-chips-chinese-firm-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国周五表示，对总部位于纽约的全球第三大代工芯片制造商 GlobalFoundries 处以 50 万美元的罚款，原因是其未经授权向被列入黑名单的中国芯片制造商中芯国际的一家子公司运送芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 18:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-penalizes-globalfoundries-shipping-chips-chinese-firm-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>委内瑞拉石油出口创四年来新高，产量增加，对美国和印度的销售增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/venezuelas-oil-exports-hit-4-year-peak-higher-output-sales-us-india-2024-11-01/</link><description>根据国有公司 PDVSA 的航运数据和文件，受原油产量增长以及对印度和美国销售增加的推动，委内瑞拉 10 月份石油出口量升至四年来新高，接近每天 95 万桶。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 16:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/venezuelas-oil-exports-hit-4-year-peak-higher-output-sales-us-india-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>萨巴伦卡力争在WTA年终总决赛上击败斯瓦泰克，年终排名第一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-aims-deny-swiatek-wta-finals-end-year-number-one-2024-11-01/</link><description>阿琳娜·萨巴伦卡 (Aryna Sabalenka) 可以通过确保年终世界排名第一的成绩来结束一个精彩的赛季，而伊加·斯瓦泰克 (Iga Swiatek) 则将在周六于沙特阿拉伯举行的 WTA 年终总决赛中占据中心舞台，并着眼于后期飙升重新夺回榜首位置。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 15:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-aims-deny-swiatek-wta-finals-end-year-number-one-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国将免签政策扩大到韩国等9个国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-visa-free-policy-9-more-countries-including-south-korea-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，中国将向韩国、挪威和芬兰等另外九个国家的公民提供免签入境政策。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 13:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-visa-free-policy-9-more-countries-including-south-korea-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国确认欧盟代表团访问进行电动汽车关税谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-confirms-eu-delegation-visit-ev-tariff-talks-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国商务部周五证实，欧盟将派代表来华就电动汽车关税争端中的价格承诺进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 12:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-confirms-eu-delegation-visit-ev-tariff-talks-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国特使在俄中北极军事合作中看到一些“令人担忧的信号”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-sees-some-concerning-signals-russia-china-military-cooperation-arctic-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国北极大使表示，美国正在密切关注俄罗斯和中国在北极地区日益增长的合作，两国最近在该地区的一些军事合作发出了“令人担忧的信号”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 12:26:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-sees-some-concerning-signals-russia-china-military-cooperation-arctic-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国与斯洛伐克在欧盟贸易争端中建立更紧密的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-underscores-benefits-cooperation-with-slovakia-during-ficos-visit-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国和斯洛伐克周五表示，他们将加强贸易和投资关系，并在罗伯特·菲科总理访问北京以建立新的战略伙伴关系期间谈到了乌克兰和平的必要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 11:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-underscores-benefits-cooperation-with-slovakia-during-ficos-visit-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚马逊安抚情绪，工资到期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-01/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 10:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，中国希望美国无论谁赢得大选，都将继续在气候变化问题上合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-hopes-us-will-continue-climate-change-collaboration-whoever-wins-election-2024-11-01/</link><description>一位政府高级官员周五表示，无论下周总统选举结果如何，中国希望美国能够继续在气候变化问题上与其他国家合作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 10:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-hopes-us-will-continue-climate-change-collaboration-whoever-wins-election-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>受制裁打击的中国科技行业对特朗普和哈里斯总统任期的影响感到困惑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-sanction-hit-tech-industry-puzzles-over-impact-trump-harris-presidencies-2024-11-01/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普下周赢得美国总统职位将比卡马拉·哈里斯获胜更让中国科技公司的前景变得混乱，高管们表示，他不可预测的风格可能会导致受到制裁打击的行业得到缓和，就像增加限制一样。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 08:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-sanction-hit-tech-industry-puzzles-over-impact-trump-harris-presidencies-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金庆祝活动引发印度购买热潮，但成交量滞后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-trigger-buying-spree-india-volumes-lag-2024-11-01/</link><description>印度的黄金需求本周因节日采购而猛增，但由于价格创历史新高，成交量低于平时。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 07:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-trigger-buying-spree-india-volumes-lag-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：值得纪念的十一月......</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-01/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 05:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国转向美国农产品进口有助于抵御贸易战风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国自2018年以来努力改变粮食进口来源，这使得如果美国总统大选后中美贸易摩擦爆发，中国更有能力对美国农产品征收针锋相对的关税，同时减少对中国粮食安全的损害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 04:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>